<br>
Usually a warrior.  In situations where very high taunt is required, a shadowknight or paladin may be used, however a warrior with defensive needs a much slower Complete heal .<br>
<br>
Jobs- Tag from the puller, take agro, call assist messages, determine targets.<br>
<br>
Secondary Assist<br>
<br>
Also useually a warrior.  Ready to function as main assist if the main goes down.  Usually the tank mezer in case of unmezable adds.<br>
